name: Homens Pelados com Objetos de Metal
description: Homens Pelados com Objetos de Metal (Naked Men with Metal Objects)is a digital painting made for the PUPILA DILATADA exhibiton.  This piece signifies a comeback to ideals of the past, in the art and life of the author, to live, create energy and movement trough calm and playful meditation.  Made by LAMA  Digital painting. 2452x2692 px.
